     <h2 class="page_title">The Loquacity Project is Born</h2>

     <p class="normal">
        Welcome to the project website for the <a href="http://www.loquacity.info">Loquacity</a> project. <a href="http://www.loquacity.info">Loquacity</a> is a simplified blogging
        application, suited for non-technical and technical users alike. Its aim is to remain simple, yet
        powerful. Loquacity enables you to talk to the world in an easy way, using the method you
        prefer: text, audio, visual and more.
     </p>
     <p class="normal">
        Based on the <a href="http://www.bblog.com">bBlog</a> blog engine, Loquacity is a furtherance of
        the project under new leadership and vision. We thank eadz and the original <a href="http://www.bblog.com">bBlog</a>
        developers for the fine foundation of ideas and effort they composited in <a href="http://www.bblog.com">bBlog</a>.
     </p>
